data.description: Welcome Home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is now available for sale. With a spacious layout and a size of 1974 square feet, this property offers plenty of room for comfortable living. The kitchen features elegant granite countertops, perfect for preparing delicious meals. Cozy up in front of the wood-burning fireplace on chilly evenings, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Conveniently located near shopping centers and restaurants, you'll have easy access to all your daily needs. This property also boasts a 3-car garage and an electric gated entry, providing both security and convenience. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a beautiful home in a desirable location. Schedule your showing today and make this house your new home!
